\frametitle{Technical evaluation: Limitations}
\begin{columns}[T]
        \begin{column}{0.6\textwidth}
            \small
            \textbf{Limitations}:
            \begin{itemize}
                \item \textbf{Dataset dependency}: Episodic meta-learning requires massive and highly diverse source datasets.
                \item \textbf{Spatial-only modality}: Ignores temporal cues, vulnerable to video replays.
                \item \textbf{Auxiliary supervision}: The method heavily relies on an auxiliary Depth Estimator.
                \item \textbf{Compactness assumption}: Genuine faces with extreme structural variance (e.g., severe poses) can fall out of $D_{rr}$, causing false rejections.
            \end{itemize}
        \end{column}
        \begin{column}{0.4\textwidth}
            \vspace{-1.5em}
            \begin{figure}
